00:23:26.939 --> 00:23:32.300
you set up your interview to allow them to use AI? Gabriela, I see the wheels turning.

00:23:32.300 --> 00:23:40.859
Yeah, it's because I worked with a few startups. I was hiring for them this year in particular,

00:23:41.579 --> 00:23:50.380
and we allowed them to use whatever tool they wanted. It's almost like an open book,

00:23:50.380 --> 00:23:57.500
but it doesn't mean that the coding was less. They could use any tool that they wanted,

00:23:57.500 --> 00:24:04.619
