00:24:04.619 --> 00:24:09.900
they would have time, they would not have time to go to the AI. They would have to ask me. So

00:24:09.900 --> 00:24:14.300
like there are a lot of signals that we are trying to get. Can you use these AI tools,

00:24:14.300 --> 00:24:21.660
