00:24:21.660 --> 00:24:26.619
guide me through your thinking process as well? So we are trying to measure two things. So like,

00:24:26.619 --> 00:24:33.819
can you use these AI tools to help you accelerate some of the questions or the answer for the

00:24:33.819 --> 00:24:38.699
